headline: Should Jabil’s New Eagle Harbour Semiconductor Partnership Require Action From Jabil (JBL) Investors?
summary: On January 20, 2026, Jabil announced a manufacturing partnership and strategic minority investment with Eagle Harbour Technologies to enhance advanced semiconductor fabrication capabilities and broaden its SEMI-compliant power solutions offering. This move deepens Jabil’s presence in semiconductor capital equipment, potentially strengthening its role as a key manufacturing partner for next-generation chip and power technologies.
